                    </span>
                            <span
                        class="icon icon-email-circle-solid social-icon padding-8-right"
                      >
                          <a href="mailto:?subject&#x3D;Zcash%20Discloses%20Vulnerability%20That%20Could%20Have%20Allowed%20&#x27;Infinite%20Counterfeit&#x27;%20Cryptocurrency%20&amp;body&#x3D;http://fortune.com/2019/02/05/zcash-vulnerability-cryptocurrency/%3Futm_source&#x3D;emailshare%26utm_medium&#x3D;email%26utm_campaign&#x3D;email-share-article%26utm_content&#x3D;20190404"
